  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6999.9 sitting directly at the massive 7000 gamma wall (21.2B), dealers are aggressively selling into this strength to hedge their long gamma positions. The PIN regime combined with this monster positive gamma barrier creates a ceiling effect here, with dealers providing heavy supply on any push above 7000. Watch for rejection at 7000-7025 range where consecutive positive gamma walls total over 30B, while support should emerge on any dip toward the 6874 flip strike.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect strong resistance and potential reversal right here at the 7000 level.",
